    {
      "name": "1.3 Status webhook (delivered)",
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json", "type": "text" }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n  \"object\": \"whatsapp_business_account\",\n  \"entry\": [{\n    \"id\": \"ACCOUNT_ID\",\n    \"changes\": [{\n      \"field\": \"messages\",\n      \"value\": {\n        \"messaging_product\": \"whatsapp\",\n        \"metadata\": {\n          \"display_phone_number\": \"3131111111\",\n          \"phone_number_id\": \"{{PHONE_NUMBER_ID}}\"\n        },\n        \"statuses\": [{\n          \"id\": \"wamid.test.001\",\n          \"status\": \"delivered\",\n          \"timestamp\": \"1748000000\",\n          \"recipient_id\": \"{{SENDER_PHONE}}\"\n        }]\n      }\n    }]\n  }]\n}",
          "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "{{BASE_URL}}/webhook",
          "host": ["{{BASE_URL}}"],
          "path": ["webhook"]
        },
        "description": "Testa o caminho value.statuses → handleStatus no app.js.\nUsa o campo 'statuses' em vez de 'messages'.\n\nO id 'wamid.test.001' não está no cache Redis → handleStatus ignora silenciosamente.\nResposta HTTP: 200 EVENT_RECEIVED (assíncrono — sem mensagem no WhatsApp).\n\nPara testar o follow-up real, seria necessário marcar uma mensagem com markMessageForFollowUp() — atualmente inativo no código."
      },
      "response": []
    },
